{"tid":712903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港樓市就嚟冧！！！中國人買樓勁蝕175萬！！！","createTime":"2018-06-22T12:53:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T14:07:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3c0eb456d2776c72ee13d3de19d38bc97a7fae38","tid":712903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T12:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/22/205301_679c772723b36d3853effed443232861.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F22%2F205301_679c772723b36d3853effed443232861.png&h=8046870f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n儘管樓市大旺，但屋苑仍錄零星蝕讓成交！業主持有的屯門星堤3座一個複式戶，實用面積1,874方呎，以1,920萬港元連車位登記沽出，呎價10,245元。上址為原業主於2011年以約2,035萬元購入，2013年再以70萬元買入車位，帳面現蝕約185萬元。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，筲箕灣譽‧東亦錄得明賺實蝕個案，該屋苑高層B室，實用面積670方呎，以1,230萬元登記轉售，呎價18,358元。據了解，原業主於2011年以逾1,204萬元買入單位，期內僅升值約2.1%，若扣除釐印及佣金等開支，料有機會損手。"},{"pid":"260b43b4f8460e4cee84b66b49a9f2c963cde82d","tid":712903,"uid":190540,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"66d7ba675130da9c17da5faa34973172949a33c4","tid":712903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T13:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59d18fdfdb1ab623c80848c0d378c113e560be6","tid":712903,"uid":11148,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T13:15:00.000Z","msg":"黑錢變白錢渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a369dff578b455589e93ee29eb7dbff97757d1e3","tid":712903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T13:57:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd760adfdad07fbd7fee357a622a79c257fce11","tid":712903,"uid":176366,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"你信唔信等等就有打手洗post<img s